product.bullet_points:
• 50-85 inches TV Stand: FITUEYES Tall TV stand is compatible with most 50 55 60 65 70 75 80 85 inches large LCD/LED Flat Curved Screens TVs .Please make sure your TV's VESA mounting holes fall between 100(w)x100(h) to 800(w)x400(h) mm. Weight capacity up to 110 lbs
• Height Adjustment & 70 Degree Swivel Mount: There are height adjustment in this 85 Inches tall TV Stand for living room and bedroom. Meanwhile, this corner TV stand could swivel left and right 35 degrees to provide you a better viewing angles while watching TV
• Metal Base with Cool Strip: This black corner TV stand constitutes sturdy pole and stable metal base, which comes with a cool strip for base decoration and brings you a sense of sleek design
• Easy to Assemble & Safety Design: This tall TV stand make of high quality steel, and safety "Bracket Lock" design to protect your TV from falling down or slipping aside. BTW, you can easily assemble by yourself with step by step instructions, and do not need to drill holes in your beautiful wall
• Cable Management & Adjustable Shelf: The corner TV stands open up your space in living room, bedroom and etc. The cable management can help you easily organize your wires on the back of the pole. The flexible media shelf is wide enough to hold your Audio Video Accessories such as DVR DVD Players Cable Boxes Consoles Satellite XBox PS3
